The paper deals with the development of a data-driven linearized AC power flow model using regression analysis. The paper is likely to belong to the Control Systems (cs.SY) category as it deals with modeling and analysis of power systems. Additionally, the use of regression analysis techniques suggests that the paper may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper may also be relevant to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category as it deals with optimization of power systems. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) category as it deals with the development of mathematical models for power systems.
